platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Think you know solitaire? Think again. Stack cards to cast spells and rid your wizard school of ghosts, mandrakes and more.
你認為自己很擅長玩接龍嗎？這款遊戲能顛覆你的想像：堆疊卡牌，施展咒語，消滅巫師學校中的鬼魂和曼德拉草等奇怪現象。
Think you know solitaire? Think again. Stack cards to cast spells and rid your wizard school of ghosts, mandrakes, and more.
